<taxonomicName id="B3CD75EEFFCAFFBDFE11E285FDE13A98" box="[389,549,1428,1451]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="460" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rancaguensis">
<emphasis id="46B9D27FFFCAFFBDFE11E285FDE13A98" box="[389,549,1428,1451]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="460">M. rancaguensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male, ventral view showing pilose hypostomal area; (e) 
<taxonomicName id="B3CD75EEFFCAFFBDFF34E2A0FEE23AFB" authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1908" box="[160,294,1457,1480]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="460" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="leucografa">
<emphasis id="46B9D27FFFCAFFBDFF34E2A0FEE23AFB" box="[160,294,1457,1480]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="460">M. leucografa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, female, hind tarsus; lines indicate measurements of length and width of basitarsus; (f) 
<taxonomicName id="B3CD75EEFFCAFFBDFF2FE2DFFEF43AD6" authorityName="Jorgensen" authorityYear="1912" box="[187,304,1486,1509]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="460" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="obscurior">
<emphasis id="46B9D27FFFCAFFBDFF2FE2DFFEF43AD6" box="[187,304,1486,1509]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="460">M. obscurior</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male, dorsal view of apical metasomal terga. Scale bars: a, e = 0.5 mm; b–d, f = 1 mm.
</paragraph>
